        -------
        
        0.1.5
        ~~~~~
        
        -  added Angle class to ext:
        -  checking of existence of files
        -  map rotation
        -  getting top or bottom of map
        -  basic arithmetics on maps
        -  map masking
        -  bugs fixes
        
